ðŸ”¹ Endpoints - Usuarios (users)
| MÃ©todo | Ruta                        | ParÃ¡metros                | Body                                        | Response                                                    |
| ------ | --------------------------- | ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- |
| POST   | `/users/`                   | -                         | `{ name, email, password, role?, status? }` | `{ id, name, email, role, status, created_at, last_login }` |
| GET    | `/users/`                   | Query: `role?`, `status?` | -                                           | Array de usuarios                                           |
| GET    | `/users/{user_id}`          | Path: `user_id`           | -                                           | `{ id, name, email, role, status, created_at, last_login }` |
| PATCH  | `/users/{user_id}`          | Path: `user_id`           | `{ name?, email?, role?, status? }`         | `{ id, name, email, role, status, created_at, last_login }` |
| DELETE | `/users/{user_id}`          | Path: `user_id`           | -                                           | 204 No Content                                              |
| POST   | `/users/{user_id}/password` | Path: `user_id`           | `{ action, old_password?, new_password? }`  | `{}`                                                        |

