ðŸ”¹ Endpoints - Permisos (permissions)
| MÃ©todo | Ruta                                    | ParÃ¡metros            | Body                                                           | Response                                                                           |
| ------ | --------------------------------------- | --------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| GET    | `/permissions/`                         | -                     | -                                                              | Array de permisos `{ id, user_id, company_id, subfolder_id, can_read, can_write }` |
| POST   | `/permissions/`                         | -                     | `{ user_id, company_id, subfolder_id, can_read?, can_write? }` | `{ id, user_id, company_id, subfolder_id, can_read, can_write }`                   |
| GET    | `/permissions/user/{user_id}`           | Path: `user_id`       | -                                                              | Array de permisos de un usuario                                                    |
