| DELETE | `/permissions/{permission_id}`          | Path: `permission_id` | -                                                              | 204 No Content                                                                     |

ðŸ”¹ Endpoints - Pedidos (orders)
| MÃ©todo | Ruta                           | ParÃ¡metros         | Body                                | Response                                                             |
| ------ | ------------------------------ | ------------------ | ----------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| GET    | `/orders/`                     | -                  | -                                   | Array de pedidos `{ id, user_id, company_id, details?, created_at }` |
| POST   | `/orders/`                     | -                  | `{ user_id, company_id, details? }` | `{ id, user_id, company_id, details?, created_at }`                  |
| GET    | `/orders/user/{user_id}`       | Path: `user_id`    | -                                   | Array de pedidos por usuario                                         |
| GET    | `/orders/company/{company_id}` | Path: `company_id` | -                                   | Array de pedidos por empresa                                         |
| GET    | `/orders/{order_id}`           | Path: `order_id`   | -                                   | `{ id, user_id, company_id, details?, created_at }`                  |
| PATCH  | `/orders/{order_id}`           | Path: `order_id`   | `{ details? }`                      | `{ id, user_id, company_id, details?, created_at }`                  |
| DELETE | `/orders/{order_id}`           | Path: `order_id`   | -                                   | 204 No Content                                                       |


ðŸ”¹ Notas importantes

Todos los endpoints que requieren seguridad (OAuth2PasswordBearer) deben recibir el header:
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
